  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>Ancestry boosts need to match what you had before turning to a vampire.</p><p>You need to feed on others' life sources by using @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.49F65W6VwuXhmv8K], @UUID[Compendium.foundryvtt-pf2e-vamps-and-dhamps.actions.Item.45qG1dMfitsS0MoK], @UUID[Compendium.foundryvtt-pf2e-vamps-and-dhamps.actions.Item.q07o5pCh5CVhtX6W], or @UUID[Compendium.foundryvtt-pf2e-vamps-and-dhamps.actions.Item.rz0llfgpFyUDedjv] depending on your heritage. If you do not feed for 3 days, you become @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.4D2KBtexWXa6oUMR]{Drained 1}. The Drained value from hunger increases each day until you successfully feed and reduces by one each time you feed. If you reach Drained 5 from hunger, you are @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.yblD8fOR1J8rDwEQ] with no saving throw until you feed. If you reach Drained 7 from hunger, you are destroyed.</p>"
    },
